'''Diskriminieshan''' a chriitment ar kansidarieshan, ar distingshan for ar gens, poersn ar ting bies pah di gruup, klaas, ar kiatigari we sed poerson ar ting posiiv se deh bilangx tu reda dah pah indivijual merit.<ref>discrimination, definition [http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/discrimination] March 2015</ref> Dis ingkluud chriitment a wah indivijual ar gruup, bies pah deh akchual ar posiiv membaship ina soertn gruup ar suoshal kiatigari, "ina wie we wos dah di wie piipl yuujali chriit".<ref>discrimination, definition [http://dictionary.cambridge.org/dictionary/american-english/discrimination] Cambridge Dictionaries Online, Cambridge University, access 29 March 2013</ref> It invalv di gruup inishal riakshan ar intarakshan gwain aan fi influens di indivijual akchual biyevia tuwadz di gruup liida ar di gruup, rischrik memba a wan gruup frah apachuniti ar privilij we avielebl tu wah nex gruup, liid tu di exkluujan a di indivijual ar entiti bies pah lajikal ar irashanal disijan mekin.<ref>Introduction to sociology. 7th ed. New York: W. W. Norton & Company Inc, 2009. p. 334.</ref>


